      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? This car is an absolute gem and in truly incredible shape\u2014seriously, it's been babied since day one! It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and I\u2019m so excited for it to find a new home. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
